error.message: Parameter $pathAliasManager of method Drupal\domain_301_redirect\EventSubscriber\DomainRedirectEventSubscriber::__construct() has typehint with deprecated interface Drupal\Core\Path\AliasManagerInterface. Deprecated in drupal:8.8.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\path_alias\AliasManagerInterface.
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to domain_301_redirect.info.yml to designate that the module is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://www.drupal.org/node/3070687.
